#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/chebyshev.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.chebyshev.chebdiv:4
msgid ""
"Returns the quotient-with-remainder of two Chebyshev series `c1` / `c2`.  "
"The arguments are sequences of coefficients from lowest order \"term\" to "
"highest, e.g., [1,2,3] represents the series ``T_0 + 2*T_1 + 3*T_2``."
msgstr ""

